      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, approved\n\nI'm in agreement that this patch will fix the current problem with updating \"..\" during rename, and should be landed.\n\nHowever, there is a lot of complexity in the \"..\" update code, and I think it needs to be cleaned up more thoroughly.  I've updated LU-2638 with some more details, and I think that should be done in a separate patch.",
